VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (Runtime(\s)*\.getRuntime(\s)*(\.|->)exec|ProcessBuilder(\s)*(\.|->)start)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(getParameter|requestParameters|System\.getProperty|args\[) && MISSING:(allowlist|whitelist)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potential command injection vulnerabilities in Java code.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Command Injection.
